source.name: NCPC Central Files Information System database (CFIS)
source.description: This dataset contains records from NCPC's Central Files Information System (CFIS). CFIS is a comprehensive database of projects submitted to NCPC for design review by federal and local agencies. The databse also contains records pertaining to NCPC's own planning initiatives.
